"compression. The default is 1."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/device-mapper/vdo.rst:134
msgid "hash:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/device-mapper/vdo.rst:135
msgid ""
"The number of threads used to manage data comparisons for deduplication "
"based on the hash value of data blocks. The default is 0."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/device-mapper/vdo.rst:139
msgid "logical:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/device-mapper/vdo.rst:140
msgid ""
"The number of threads used to manage caching and locking based on the "
"logical address of incoming bios. The default is 0; the maximum is 60."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/device-mapper/vdo.rst:144
msgid "physical:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/device-mapper/vdo.rst:145
msgid ""
"The number of threads used to manage administration of the underlying "
"storage device. At format time, a slab size for the vdo is chosen; the vdo "
"storage device must be large enough to have at least 1 slab per physical "
"thread. The default is 0; the maximum is 16."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/device-mapper/vdo.rst:151
